longBusinessSummary: Future Science Holdings Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, the company was engaged in the exploration and development of titanium deposits or reserves in Chile. Future Science Holdings Inc. was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Santiago, Chile.
